text: Harry Céspedes (born 27 July 1998) is a Bolivian footballer who plays for Royal Pari F.C. in the Bolivian Primera División. On 16 November 2018 he made his debut for the Bolivia national football team against the U.A.E. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Bolivian footballers Category:Bolivia international footballers Category:Association footballers not categorized by position
